high_descs: Walk across the room to the dining table.

high_descs: Pick up the closest cardboard box.
Turn left and head to the wall then turn right to face the lamp.

Turn the off the lamp next to the red sofa.

high_descs: Grab the box closest to the right of the gold statue
Take the box and move to the light that is on by the red sofa
